Mountain God,

00:02:49.865 --> 00:02:50.904
sorry for disturbing you.

00:02:51.145 --> 00:02:52.464
I'm just here to find my dog.

00:02:52.464 --> 00:02:53.585
I'll leave once I find him.

00:03:10.865 --> 00:03:11.705
Dandan?

00:03:12.504 --> 00:03:13.425
Dandan?

00:03:14.105 --> 00:03:15.105
Wait for me.

00:03:15.585 --> 00:03:16.744
I'm coming to save you.

00:03:41.464 --> 00:03:42.344
Dandan?

